high_descs: Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Take the cup out of the fridge.
Turn around and go all the way left to the microwave.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Turn around and walk straight to the table, then right to the fridge.
Place the cup in the fridge to the right of the fruit.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup in a fridge.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and remove the white cup that is inside the fridge, then close the door.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk over to to the microwave.
Put the white cup in the microwave and turn it on, after a couple seconds take the cup out and close the microwave door.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Put the heated white cup in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated white cup in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the door and remove the cup from the shelf.
Turn around to the right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the cup inside, close the microwave. Start the microwave. Open the microwave, remove the cup, close the microwave.
Turn to the left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the cup inside, close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm cup in the refrigerator.
